      <title>对欧洲来说，下一任美国总统既是冲击也是变革的催化剂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/trump-s-second-term-could-be-a-disaster-for-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普的第二届政府对该地区来说似乎是一场灾难。它也可能最终让非洲大陆摆脱沉闷的状态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/trump-s-second-term-could-be-a-disaster-for-europe</guid>
