    <item>
      <title>随着战争持续，乌克兰对军队的捐赠减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/as-war-grinds-on-ukrainians-donate-less-to-their-military</link>
      <description><![CDATA[私人对乌克兰军事行动的捐款大幅下降，表明在唐纳德·特朗普连任后，这个饱受战争蹂躏的国家对未来持谨慎态度，乌克兰人为国防做出贡献的意愿正在减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/as-war-grinds-on-ukrainians-donate-less-to-their-military</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
